weloveclouds.server.services.datastore.models

Class DataAccessServiceInitializationContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • weloveclouds.server.services.datastore.models.DataAccessServiceInitializationContext

  • public class DataAccessServiceInitializationContext
extends java.lang.Object
    An initialization context object which stores those parameters that are neccessary for the correct behavior of a DataAccessService. E.g.:
    (1) size of the cache,
    (2) displacement startegy to be used in the cache,
    (3) path for the PersistedStorageUnit where it stores the entries.
